                        <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Week 1: Planning & Decluttering</h4>
                        <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">Plan your approach, gather supplies, and declutter each room before deep cleaning begins.</p>
