                    <div style="background: #f8fafa; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="background: #ff8057; color: white; width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1rem; font-weight: bold;">2</div>
                        <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Week 2: Deep Clean Bedrooms & Bathrooms</h4>
