                                <li>Organize pantry and check expiration dates</li>
                                <li>Deep clean backsplash and grout</li>
                                <li>Polish countertops and seal natural stone</li>
                                <li>Clean light fixtures and ceiling fan</li>
                                <li>Mop and seal floor, especially grout lines</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="background: #f8fafa; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid #ff8057;">
