                                <li>Deep clean upholstered furniture</li>
                                <li>Vacuum and flip mattresses</li>
                                <li>Wash all bedding, pillows, and comforters</li>
                                <li>Steam clean carpets and rugs</li>
                                <li>Dust and condition wood furniture</li>
                                <li>Clean and organize closets completely</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div>
                            <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Air Quality & Details</h4>
                            <ul style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8; padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                                <li>Replace HVAC filters throughout home</li>
                                <li>Clean air vents and return ducts</li>
                                <li>Dust all surfaces, baseboards, and trim</li>
