                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">Gathering the right supplies ensures efficient and effective spring cleaning. According to <a href="https://www.cdc.gov/hygiene/cleaning/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #ff8057; text-decoration: none;">CDC cleaning guidelines</a>, proper disinfectants and cleaning techniques are essential for maintaining a healthy home environment. The <a href="https://www.epa.gov/indoor-air-quality-iaq" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #ff8057; text-decoration: none;">EPA's indoor air quality standards</a> also emphasize the importance of proper ventilation during and after cleaning.</p>
                
